      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 1987 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2 is a mechanically sorted driver-spec example featuring the desirable G50 Getrag 5-speed manual transaxle. The longitudinal 3.2L flat-six delivers linear power through Bosch Motronic engine management, exhibiting consistent compression and optimal oil pressure across the operating range. The chassis retains its original torsion bar suspension geometry, providing the visceral feedback and communicative steering rack characteristic of the G-body platform. Equipped with staggered Fuchs alloy wheels and ventilated disc brakes, the vehicle offers sharp turn-in and reliable stopping power. While the finish shows honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and underpinnings are robust, having recently undergone a valve adjustment and a comprehensive inspection of the oil cooling circuit.",
